						<summary>

						<p>Slab built into the platform infront of the Kēśava temple.</p>						

						<p>17th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This undated record may be assigned to the 17th century on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>Registers a gift of land measuring five <hi rend="italic">munt tas</hi> (specified) made for the construction of a <hi rend="italic">śikhara.</hi></p>						

